Interface SapaProcessor.MessageListener

  • Enclosing class:
    SapaProcessor

    public static interface SapaProcessor.MessageListener
    This listener interface provides callback methods to receive messages and data from the processing module.
    Since:
    Samsung Android JellyBean
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    HaeSeok Oh, LaeHyuk Bang, JeongYeon Kim, DaeBeom Park

    • Method Summary

      Methods

    • Method Detail

      • onMessageReceived

        void onMessageReceived(int id,
                     String message)
        Called when a message is received from the processing module.
        The messages are not defined in the Professional Audio package.
        For information on the message format, see the relevant manual for the processing module plug-in.
        Parameters:
        id - The message ID.
        message - The message from the processing module.

      • onDataReceived

        void onDataReceived(int id,
                  ByteBuffer data)
        Called when data is received from the processing module.
        The data format is not defined in the Professional Audio package.
        For more information on the data format, see the relevant manual for the processing module plug-in.
        Parameters:
        id - The data ID.
        data - The data from the processing module.
